data.description: Wow! Here is your chance to own in the Southwest area and still be incredibly convenient to everything you need in Asheboro. You will love this 3 bed/2 bath brick home in Oakwood Acres. The amazing fireplace commands the living room. And the exposed beams are a nice touch as well. Kitchen has been updated with granite and stainless appliances. New roof in 2022 (50 yr shingle). New well pump installed 2 yrs ago. Washer and dryer remain. Come find your dream home.
